text: Abdul Hamid Mohammed Dbeibeh (), born February 13, 1958, is a Libyan politician. He is the current Prime Minister of Libya since 2021. In September 2021, the Parliament votes the motion of censure against the government of Abdel Hamid Dbeibah. In November 2021, Abdul Hamid Dbeibeh, presented his candidacy for President of Libya in the upcoming election. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Libya
title: Abdul Hamid Dbeibeh
